Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I borrowed this mansion from\nmy uncle to give music lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I had no idea that there was\na room like this in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, that crazy uncle of mine sure collected\nlots of useless junk from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... What what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Watchman of the New Moon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Barat mint leaves are smashed\nand mixed into water..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A melody is materializing in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This fragrance is... mint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&H61AAA6&}~ Midsummer Night's Dream ~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken on a new pupil to\nprepare her for an audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of things for me again, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, Haruto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-san, will you be giving Ichigo-chan and\nyour new student "special" lessons, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the talent for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely understand how these\nlessons benefit the students,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm concerned that if your\nmethods leaked out to the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it might cause a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that happened, we can just\nsay they made it up to frame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I compose good music and sell it to their artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all they care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's your attitude as you continue\nto chase after "perfection", isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Perfection", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say it like that I get\nthe feeling it's a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just me being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My actions are restricting your career\nas an independent composer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished for this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cum as many times as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the least I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's plenty for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-san, what's that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've heard it somewhere before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You usually never forget a phrase once you've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this room isn't really set up for dining alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it allows you to consume the vast\nquantities of food you need all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, it works out nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's another way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a child, your body has amazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in your thin body does all that food go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as your personal assistant I must speak\nto you about a job-related maner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not certain you should take on that new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bothering me in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave aside the fact that she has amnesia\nand doesn't know her family origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying she's from the Kaon family in\norder to promote her is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not germane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize that she has musical talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that matters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering your back is also part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the lesson room has been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion-kun, you're first rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so skilled that it was a waste\nfor you to be my uncles butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you'd graduate from being\na cherry boy, you'd be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0h, Master, why must you always tease me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've worn clothes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were naked the first time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after seeing you like this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd look better with\na little more mass in your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's Master for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint-san, please understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-sama doesn't have ulterior motives or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you don't hold his behavior against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Master, since Mint's full name is Mitsuishi Mint,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to say that she's my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just don't use your position to\ntake advantage of her, Shion-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you always jump to conclusions, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-sama really means no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, Ichigo is berry cute today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I get to do my first performance with Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a perfect opportunity to\nsolidify my bond with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song was perfect Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like the gentle whisper of an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It paralyzed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It granted me the peace of a green forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I cant even find the words to express\nhow beautiful your song was, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo still needs many more lessons from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a private lesson right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me a good lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to cross the threshold into adulthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo had better work hard at her lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me, Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be enriching for both of us, Mint-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan? Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new pupil, Mitsuishi Mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mitsuishi Mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"N-New pupil"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, a new character in the series?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning a new love interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning I have to share my screen time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, my rank goes down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...until I'm just a boring supporting character?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Onii-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she's your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I mean, I just call him that to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, maybe I should also\nrefer to Sensei that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of the characters is allowed to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oizumi Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet'cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a delicious-sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a newcomer here, so any help you could\ngive me would be much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Mint-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so the custom in this country is to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's girls for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They become friends so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-san, I don't think that's quite what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess she's so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I guess if Onii-chan\npicked her, it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not bad at this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she's still no match for the great Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your running pace is uneven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, stupid Mint! I'm sick of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a few days of lessons,\nwhat's your impression of Mint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does she have high musical aptitude,\nbut her dedication to training is admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your perception is quite accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from you makes me\nfeel even more secure, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah, to think I call her Sakura-Oneechan,\nall respectful-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid four-eyed bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through a lot of trouble to make myself\nthe bratty-yet-lovable little sister character!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm gonna share that\nposition nicely with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't that kind of anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! That's your fault too, Mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, Onii-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Onii-chan will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the winner is... entry number 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oizumi Ichigo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warm applause from all of my\nbeloved fans is my pride and joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep this to myself any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you form a unit with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, could you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lesson starts soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come to the practice room with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt my fantasy when\nit's getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I definitely won't let you have my Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taking lessons with Onii-chan\nlong before you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the early bird catches the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. So Ichigo-chan loves him too.
