Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.39,0:25:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I suck a man's life force away,\nhe usually takes at least a week to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.19,0:25:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint, your voice when you were\ncumming just then was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.27,0:25:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Sensei? It's about my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you still have that sensation in\nyour body, try singing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For real, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.58,0:25:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a freaking demon, you know? A demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.25,0:25:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends here, Mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil spirit, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.71,0:25:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Onii-chan at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.25,0:25:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.05,0:25:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, well I just thought I'd\nmatch the mood of this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:26:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Never mind me. It's Mint who looks weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, aren't you freaked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.52,0:26:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my place to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.89,0:26:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Listen to Mint sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.23,0:26:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to hear just how much she's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.77,0:26:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's singing you want, Ichigo can...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.65,0:26:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I'll return you to sanity with my singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.78,0:26:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the far-off darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:23.28,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.29,0:26:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the evil Suima invade the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:27.29,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.25,0:26:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.96,0:26:36.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,My once sealed off heart felt warmth for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.51,0:26:37.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,When we-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.87,0:26:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll face them with my heart on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.51,0:26:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect your, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.23,0:26:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you return to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard once before that music has\nthe power to transform demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.11,0:26:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.86,0:27:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.57,0:27:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what I do understand is that\nboth of you have improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.29,0:27:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to your auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.21,0:27:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess no matter what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you always place music at the top of your priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.13,0:27:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but I guess\nyou're right. We do need work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.26,0:27:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint! Well settle this score at our audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo-chan, are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.48,0:27:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you fair and square,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.90,0:27:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'll get Onii-chan to respect\nme as an artist and as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.66,0:27:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both nice and excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.79,0:27:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint and Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.42,0:27:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as I thought things are quite different here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:07.60,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,tada bouzen to nani ga shitai ka tte
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:07.60,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked with my mouth agape, "What do I want to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.31,0:28:11.68,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,tachi domatte sora o miageta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.31,0:28:11.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing still, I gazed up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.39,0:28:19.44,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,masshiro na kumo funwari to oyoide ita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.39,0:28:19.44,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure white clouds swam lightly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.03,0:28:27.68,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mono nani mo nai sora no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.03,0:28:27.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,What I aim for is in the empty sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:35.52,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,miezu ni tsukarete doko made yuku no oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:31.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to see it, I become exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.89,0:28:35.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Wondering how far I'll go. Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.08,0:28:40.10,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,let's take power sakende iru
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.08,0:28:40.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take power! I'm screaming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:43.99,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,tsuyosa o ima tsutaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:43.99,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to show others I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.09,0:28:47.95,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,let's take power todoite iru
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.09,0:28:47.95,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take power! I'm reaching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:54.32,Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,namida mo yorokobi ni kawaru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:54.32,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,My tears will change to joy.
